data.description: This Three bedroom 1.5 bath house is ready for you to call Home. This home gets plenty of natural light. Hardwood flooring throughout, newer roof, Nice back yard for playing and entertainment family and friends, Lower and upper patio overlooking the city. Working fireplace in the living room for a nice romantic evening on the cold winter nights. A two car detached garage, and a partially finished basement with a private entrance (turn it into your man/woman cave or additional living space. Huge Laundry/Work Room with yet another fireplace.
